item.author: wouter.groeneveld@gmail.com (Wouter Groeneveld)
item.description: Signing Compile fouten: ‘cannot import the following key file’ C:<br/>Windows<br/>Microsoft.NET<br/>Framework<br/>v4.0.30319<br/>Microsoft.Common.targets(2455, 5): error MSB3325: Cannot import the following key file: ign.pfx. The key file may be password protected. To correct this, try to import the certificate again or manually install the certificate to the Strong Name CSP with the following key container name: VS_KEY_0E36C1B21D0EBCA4 Oplossen door met sntool te registreren en die container naam aan te maken (VSKEY…) Assemblies signen Properties -> Signing -> Sign the assembly aanvinken.
